{
  "stem": "27443.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had, given in the morning-- they give us hot coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The hot coffee, we found out later, that it's poisoned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Majdanek the same way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had coffee given that it was for the women not to get their period.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I had my period, and then it stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because that coffee, we later found out, was poisoned that we shouldn't have our period.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't get my period until I was liberated, because my system was all poisoned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at Skarzysko, we had the soup and a piece of bread when we marched in from work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were 12-hour shift, working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was selected to work in [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is a certain part of the HASAG that made certain bullets, ammunition, for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was working on a shift-- 12-hour shift, that-- by a table with a lot of women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were about 30-35 women making bullets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shell.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had machines that had to fit certain sizes to make the bullet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The shell had to fit into the bullet-- into the powder-- the powder to go into the bullet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I heard a SS woman that was over us-- her name was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was just like Bartenschlager.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tall, fat, and she was very strong, tall woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she used to call me [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what did she see in me, but I was a good-- supposedly I was a good worker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she always used to send with the Polish guy that used to work with us, the manager, that she used to give me an extra piece of bread for working so good.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So in Skarzysko, I was working the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Skarzysko in 1943.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beginning '43.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked in Skarzysko in the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
